三人不法之利益，而竊佔他人之不動產者，依前\r\n項之規定處斷。\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/HLDM/111%2c%e8%8a%b1%e5%8e%9f%e7%b0%a1%2c115%2c20220921%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"HLDM,111,花原簡,115,20220921,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"花原簡","JNO":"115","JDATE":"20220921","JTITLE":"竊盜"}